{"tid":1865603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"澤尻涉毒案判有罪！獲緩刑3年不需入獄","createTime":"2020-02-06T09:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T12:32:02.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"609409de3bc36e9bbc504bd096986544b12491e9","tid":1865603,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:14:42.000Z","msg":"33歲日本女星澤尻英龍華於去年11月16日因涉毒被捕，上月31日在東京地方法院首度開庭審訊，庭上她認罪，更公布引退宣言，揚言無意及無資格復出藝能界。而檢察官要求判澤尻監禁1年半，緩刑3年。案件今日日本時間下午3時宣布判決，一如所料，澤尻被判有罪，判監禁1年半，獲緩刑3年，不用入獄。<br />\n<br />\n大批巿民一早到法院外排隊爭取法院旁聽座位，截至當地時間11時，有915人排隊爭19個座位。而上月31日首度開庭當天，有2,229名市民輪候爭取19個旁聽座位。<br />\n<br />\n去年11月16日，警方在澤尻寓所搜出0.198克搖頭丸粉末及約0.601克俗稱「毒郵票」的LDS 。其後她被控藏毒，去年12月以約36萬港元保釋後一直潛水，並入住東京慶應大學附屬醫院接受戒毒治療。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200206/bkn-20200206120817592-0206_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200206%2Fbkn-20200206120817592-0206_00862_001.html&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=5d8dcae0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200206/bkn-20200206120817592-0206_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"47cc6bdbed3c97e9affdc935bad09ee58974c11e","tid":1865603,"uid":149925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:15:25.000Z","msg":"幾時拍av?"},{"pid":"fcbc4cda1c6b69cf8ced4073120352c30c706b61","tid":1865603,"uid":32691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c8a3d46ad0b2d526f1597ae4d9ea9e80d63d2f","tid":1865603,"uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"47cc6bdbed3c97e9affdc935bad09ee58974c11e","tid":1865603,"uid":149925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:15:25.000Z","msg"